{"tid":2333172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再話大陸啲小粉紅","createTime":"2020-12-20T07:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T16:13:45.000Z","uid":258784,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ada6af32c0c9d7d0e520725f10cc4ada81960511","tid":2333172,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"今朝起身，有小小凍，就開着咗個發熱坐墊，一坐落去真係暖笠笠，好私服<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6BHZBQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BHZBQn.jpg&h=4d02ebb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係諗到大陸今年要限制用電就覺得自己身在福中不知褔，而家響大陸嘅人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">抵撚死呀！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持一隻弱智糖尿維尼統治自己，條路自己揀凍親唔好喊，<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">所以大家真係唔應該再話啲小粉紅，應該笑9佢哋</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一諗到呢度，我明明已經暖笠笠但係都忍唔住伸隻手去較高一格，打完呢個po嘅時候個屎忽已經熱到就快出汗，係<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">好熱呀！好熱呀！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然唔少得睇人仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atpdGk1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatpdGk1.jpg&h=1151f898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5E7VUF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5E7VUF4.jpg&h=d9e11e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZieqNO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZieqNO.jpg&h=4a33b5b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4x3i7O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4x3i7O.jpg&h=e44f5251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tux3i7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftux3i7P.jpg&h=a0ecec61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8ec2387420f4fb8af10836ca8e4a3b066ebe5c6","tid":2333172,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:55:52.000Z","msg":"吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67ba6cf73f3782a38f54731aa66a7cb2fc1e11e","tid":2333172,"uid":258784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ec2387420f4fb8af10836ca8e4a3b066ebe5c6","tid":2333172,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:55:52.000Z","msg":"吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"飲巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7129a2e2c5b831b839ba730caf73b654f2a83805","tid":2333172,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b67ba6cf73f3782a38f54731aa66a7cb2fc1e11e","tid":2333172,"uid":258784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ec2387420f4fb8af10836ca8e4a3b066ebe5c6","tid":2333172,"uid":51